"{\"uid\": \"standard.co.uk-sport-sport-olympics-tom-daley-olympic-medals-2024-b1173668.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"To use the search feature, we need your consent to load Google Custom Search, which may use cookies or similar technologies.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 124, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 56, \"end\": 76, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Google Custom Search\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google_Programmable_Search_Engine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Please click 'Allow and Continue' below to enable search.\", \"from\": 125, \"to\": 182, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"See our privacy policy for more information.\", \"from\": 183, \"to\": 227, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sport|Olympics  It had taken a dramatic U-turn to lureTom Daleyback to theTeam GBdiving programme.\", \"from\": 229, \"to\": 327, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sparked by his son Robbie's wish to watch his father compete at another Olympics, Daley contacted his former bosses to enquire if there was a vacancy in the 10metre synchro platform diving team.\", \"from\": 329, \"to\": 523, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 348, \"end\": 354, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robbie_Jackson\", \"score\": 0.9967124081523173, \"rank\": 0.0032984214906183512, \"text\": \"Robbie\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robbie_Jackson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robbie_Jackson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He was effectively told he could come back into the fold if Noah Williams and Matty Lee failed to win a medal at the World Championships.\", \"from\": 525, \"to\": 662, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 585, \"end\": 598, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Williams_(diver)\", \"score\": 0.999998273608197, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noah Williams\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Williams_(diver)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Williams_(diver)\"}, {\"begin\": 603, \"end\": 612, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matty_Lee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Matty Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matty_Lee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matty_Lee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They came up short and it opened the door for the 30-year-old to return, further aided when Lee had to undergo surgery.\", \"from\": 663, \"to\": 782, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 755, \"end\": 758, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\", \"score\": 0.999946148686676, \"rank\": 5.384295521970629e-05, \"text\": \"Lee\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cliff_Lee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Havingproduced a stunning performance on Monday to win silverand complete the set of Olympic medals with a gold in Tokyo and three previous bronze medals, it led to inevitable questions about his future.\", \"from\": 784, \"to\": 987, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 899, \"end\": 904, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9996191827084018, \"rank\": 0.00038002156831907916, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He talked about the last year with an enthusiasm not befitting of an athlete with fiveOlympic Gamesto his name and hinted at the possibility that Los Angeles in four years' time is not an impossibility.\", \"from\": 989, \"to\": 1191, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1135, \"end\": 1146, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999999290594, \"rank\": 5.2078985281259695e-11, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For one, it will be a home Games of sorts having uprooted with his Hollywood scriptwriter husband Dustin Lance Black and the couple's two children, Robbie and Phoenix, there.\", \"from\": 1193, \"to\": 1367, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1260, \"end\": 1269, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_the_United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 2.559559639687029e-12, \"text\": \"Hollywood\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_the_United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_the_United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1291, \"end\": 1309, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_Lance_Black\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Dustin Lance Black\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_Lance_Black\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_Lance_Black\"}, {\"begin\": 1341, \"end\": 1347, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robbie_Jackson\", \"score\": 0.9967124081523173, \"rank\": 0.0032984214906183512, \"text\": \"Robbie\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robbie_Jackson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robbie_Jackson\"}, {\"begin\": 1352, \"end\": 1359, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoenix_Raceway\", \"score\": 0.999967876505994, \"rank\": 2.6691594456177994e-05, \"text\": \"Phoenix\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoenix_Raceway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoenix_Raceway\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is talk of adding a mixed 10m competition, which could likely lead to an all-star pairing with Andrea Spendolini-Sirieix in 2028.\", \"from\": 1369, \"to\": 1504, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1470, \"end\": 1495, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrea_Spendolini-Sirieix\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Andrea Spendolini-Sirieix\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrea_Spendolini-Sirieix\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrea_Spendolini-Sirieix\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking shortly after his silver medal, he said of his future, \\\"I do not really know yet because I went from being the youngest on the team in 2008 to now being the oldest diver.\", \"from\": 1506, \"to\": 1685, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I want to kind of enjoy this moment and make a decision about my diving future later on.\", \"from\": 1686, \"to\": 1774, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Olympics 2024 medal table: Latest count today after Team GB rush on day three  \\\"They might be adding different events into Los Angeles so it could be a chance to do a second home Games now I live in LA.\\\"\", \"from\": 1776, \"to\": 1979, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1828, \"end\": 1835, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999993594285348, \"rank\": 3.656852034583922e-07, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 1899, \"end\": 1910, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999999290594, \"rank\": 5.2078985281259695e-11, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The decision over Paris was instigated by Robbie on a visit to the Olympic Museum in Colorado Springs, partly down to his father's tears when showed a video of what it meant to be an Olympian.\", \"from\": 1981, \"to\": 2173, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1999, \"end\": 2004, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999999990905, \"rank\": 9.235202470754388e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2023, \"end\": 2029, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robbie_Jackson\", \"score\": 0.9967124081523173, \"rank\": 0.0032984214906183512, \"text\": \"Robbie\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robbie_Jackson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robbie_Jackson\"}, {\"begin\": 2048, \"end\": 2062, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Museum\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Olympic Museum\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\", \"Q33506\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Museum\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Museum\"}, {\"begin\": 2066, \"end\": 2074, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colorado\", \"score\": 0.9912723411543254, \"rank\": 0.005475489896981735, \"text\": \"Colorado\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colorado\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colorado\"}, {\"begin\": 2164, \"end\": 2172, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999976345439573, \"rank\": 2.365461798102233e-06, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And Daley, who blew kisses to his husband and kids off the podium, admitted he could yet be swayed by his boys to carry on.\", \"from\": 2175, \"to\": 2298, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Robbie has already had his token used,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2300, \"to\": 2349, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2301, \"end\": 2307, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robbie_Jackson\", \"score\": 0.9967124081523173, \"rank\": 0.0032984214906183512, \"text\": \"Robbie\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robbie_Jackson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robbie_Jackson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We will see what Phoenix thinks in a few years' time.\\\"\", \"from\": 2350, \"to\": 2405, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2368, \"end\": 2375, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoenix_Raceway\", \"score\": 0.999967876505994, \"rank\": 2.6691594456177994e-05, \"text\": \"Phoenix\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoenix_Raceway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoenix_Raceway\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It had clearly not been without its issues making these Games.\", \"from\": 2407, \"to\": 2469, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For one, he and his diving partner live either side of the Atlantic and had trained for just two months together.\", \"from\": 2470, \"to\": 2583, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It begged the question what might be possible for the two, who have become good friends to the extent that Williams stayed with Daley and his family for three weeks in California earlier this year, if they trained together full-time.\", \"from\": 2585, \"to\": 2818, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2753, \"end\": 2763, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/California\", \"score\": 0.9998267899204905, \"rank\": 0.00017060830955595616, \"text\": \"California\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/California\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/California\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am so proud to come back after two years,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2820, \"to\": 2874, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Fifteen months ago, I was sitting on the sofa doing nothing.\", \"from\": 2875, \"to\": 2936, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Being able to set an example to the kids if you have a dream and work hard it does not always mean you will achieve what you want to.\", \"from\": 2938, \"to\": 3072, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But it's the happiest I have been in diving in all my years.\\\"\", \"from\": 3073, \"to\": 3134, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It makes the prospect of four more years that bit more tempting.\", \"from\": 3136, \"to\": 3200, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"MORE ABOUT  Have your say...  1  Crime  Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line train after youths told to stop vaping by middle-aged passenger  Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line after youths told to stop vaping  2  Football  Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup, confirmed team news, injury latest for Premier League today  Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup and confirmed team news  3  UK  Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning over Donald Trump's Iran war  Flights alert: UK issues global travel disruption warning on Iran war  4  Lifestyle  Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026  Horoscope today: Your daily guide for Saturday, March 21, 2026  5  Football  Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news, predicted lineup, injury latest for Carabao Cup final  Arsenal XI vs Man City: Confirmed team news and predicted lineup\", \"from\": 3202, \"to\": 4080, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3262, \"end\": 3271, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\", \"score\": 0.996829456417192, \"rank\": 0.003127986834993746, \"text\": \"Elizabeth\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\"}, {\"begin\": 3362, \"end\": 3371, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\", \"score\": 0.996829456417192, \"rank\": 0.003127986834993746, \"text\": \"Elizabeth\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\"}, {\"begin\": 3440, \"